renderedTemplate:
apiVersion: tfcontroller.contrib.fluxcd.io/v1alpha1
kind: Terraform
metadata:
  name: dev
spec:
  interval: 1h
  path: ./
  approvePlan: "auto"
  vars:
    - name: cluster_identifier
      value: cluster-name
  sourceRef:
    kind: GitRepository
    name: git-repo-name
    namespace: git-repo-namespace
